  'summary' => 'Build a personalised relapse prevention plan with warning signs, coping strategies, and who to call, before you need it.',
  'summary_sw' => 'Jenga mpango wa kuzuia kurudi kwa unyogovu na dalili za onyo, mikakati ya kukabiliana, na nani wa kupigia simu.',
  'content' => "## Why prevention matters\n\nDepression often follows a pattern. There are early warning signs that appear days or weeks before a full episode. Most people can learn to recognise their own pattern and take action early, when it is much easier.\n\n## Step 1: Know your personal warning signs\n\nCommon warning signs include: withdrawing from people without explaining why, stopping self-care basics, ruminating more than usual, losing interest in your most important values, sleeping much more or less than normal, and negative thoughts becoming more frequent.\n\nWrite down your 3 to 5 most reliable warning signs.\n\n## Step 2: Your Tier 1 responses (early signs)\n\nWhen you notice 1 to 2 warning signs, take these actions immediately: contact your therapist, schedule one behavioural activation activity per day for the next week, tell one trusted person that you are noticing something.\n\n## Step 3: Your Tier 2 responses (episode beginning)\n\nIf the episode is deepening: request an urgent session with your therapist, activate your support network honestly, reduce commitments where possible, consider whether medication should be reviewed.\n\n## Step 4: Your support people\n\nName 2 to 3 people who know about your depression and who you trust to take you seriously. For each one, write their name, their relationship to you, and what you have agreed they can do when you are struggling.\n\n## Step 5: Crisis numbers\n\nKeep a crisis line number somewhere you will find it even in a very dark moment. The SOS button on this platform connects you to a counsellor at any time. Befrienders Kenya: 0722 178 177.\n\n## The key principle\n\nYour safety net only works if it exists before the crisis. Build it now.",
  'content_sw' => "## Kwa nini kuzuia kunasaidia\n\nUnyogovu mara nyingi hufuata mfumo. Kuna dalili za mapema kabla ya kipindi kamili.\n\n## Hatua muhimu\n\n1. Jua dalili zako za onyo za kibinafsi\n2. Jibu la haraka unapoziona\n3. Watu wanaokusaidia, majina na nambari\n4. Nambari za dharura",
